mponents of a course or unit that demonstrate the capabilities, knowledge and skills to achieve the core learning outcomes of that course or unit. You will need to be able to meet these inherent requirements to complete your course.</p><p><a href="https://www.acu.edu.au/study-at-acu/how-to-apply/inherent-requirements" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Learn more about inherent requirements for your course and how they affect you</a></p> </div> </div> </div>',
